{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11331/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11331"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:13:31"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man sips tea from a bowl"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11331","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11331"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1/0b73db12-873a-46f7-a2a1-44587823de7d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:33:43.852Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds and Cyril’s quick, intense verbal skirmish is punctuated by the latter’s sips of tea. The drink continues to serve as a marker of power and conflict between characters. Cyril’s threat is ultimately enacted by Alma: Reynolds <em>will</em> end up on the floor after he is poisoned.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:627.5121951219512,357.36585365853665,364.3317073170732,344.66341463414636"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1/19070193-9fbd-4ad9-8606-ff7090557c1b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:34:17.051Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The fact that Alma poisons Reynolds’s tea is also an inversion of the maternal role that she plays in their complex relationship. She weakens him with the poison mushroom in an act that a mother might take for a sick child—preparing hot tea for them.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11331/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1067.7073170731708,392.9560975609756,263.1804878048779,221.97073170731716"}}}]}]}]}